    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In Atomic Wilds, you wake up in a post-apocalyptic world with no memory and one vague directive: discover what happened… and stop it from happening again.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore every inch of a massive, seamless overworld packed with secrets and dangers. Scavenge forgotten facilities, fight through hostile patrols, and piece together the last echoes of humanity’s final days from ancient terminals. Survival depends on what you uncover.<i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore a massive, open post-apocalyptic world!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From rusted highways and toxic mushroom forests to lava pits and frozen bunkers, every screen is hand-built with hidden secrets. Navigate traps, hazards, and terrain that challenge both your aim and your wits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693960/extras/5b502e8dfc505b9aec864529b209d3ed.poster.avif?t=1768364308\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693960/extras/5b502e8dfc505b9aec864529b209d3ed.webm?t=1768364308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693960/extras/5b502e8dfc505b9aec864529b209d3ed.mp4?t=1768364308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade your weapon and customize your bullets!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect scrap from enemies to improve your gun’s damage, fire rate, and bullet speed at upgrade stations. Discover and mix six unique bullet mods-bounce, explosion, tri-bullet, fire trails, slow effects, and homing shots-to tailor your loadout to any challenge.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693960/extras/4a1ecc6e6de973bfe2d50c08c0006564.poster.avif?t=1768364308\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693960/extras/4a1ecc6e6de973bfe2d50c08c0006564.webm?t=1768364308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693960/extras/4a1ecc6e6de973bfe2d50c08c0006564.mp4?t=1768364308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the lost facilities that now store humanity’s deepest secrets and enemies!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The path to the Master A.I. leads through seven unique dungeons packed with hazards, relics, and deadly bosses that will test your skills and upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693960/extras/957e8159afa75046df23422e05582643.poster.avif?t=1768364308\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693960/extras/957e8159afa75046df23422e05582643.webm?t=1768364308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693960/extras/957e8159afa75046df23422e05582643.mp4?t=1768364308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A massive 10x8 overworld map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 hand-crafted dungeons and bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 unique bullet mods with combinable effects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 ability chips that change how you explore and fight</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon stat upgrades to tailor your playstyle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save/load anytime</p></li></ul>",
